  2nephi,15,14,"Therefore, hell hath enlarged herself, and opened her mouth without measure; and their glory, and their multitude, and their pomp, and he that rejoiceth, shall descend into it.",""
  2nephi,15,15,"And the mean man shall be brought down, and the mighty man shall be humbled, and the eyes of the lofty shall be humbled.","26:33:Isa. 2:17 (11, 17).|48:54:2 Ne. 12:11.|97:102:TG Haughtiness."
