  2nephi,21,13,"The envy of Ephraim also shall depart, and the adversaries of Judah shall be cut off; Ephraim shall not envy Judah, and Judah shall not vex Ephraim.","4:8:Jer. 3:18.|104:108:Ezek. 37:22 (16–22). TG Envy.|109:114:TG Israel, Joseph, People of; Israel, Judah, People of."
