  2nephi,21,15,"And the Lord shall utterly destroy the tongue of the Egyptian sea; and with his mighty wind he shall shake his hand over the river, and shall smite it in the seven streams, and make men go over dry shod.","27:34:Zech. 10:11.|194:197:Rev. 16:12."
