  2nephi,22,3,"Therefore, with joy shall ye draw water out of the wells of salvation.","34:39:TG Living Water."
  2nephi,22,4,"And in that day shall ye say: Praise the Lord, call upon his name, declare his doings among the people, make mention that his name is exalted.","30:36:TG Praise; Thanksgiving."
