  2nephi,23,6,"Howl ye, for the day of the Lord is at hand; it shall come as a destruction from the Almighty.","17:20:TG Day of the Lord."
  2nephi,23,7,"Therefore shall all hands be faint, every man's heart shall melt;","60:64:Jer. 9:7; D&C 133:41."
  2nephi,23,8,And they shall be afraid; pangs and sorrows shall take hold of them; they shall be amazed one at another; their faces shall be as flames.,""
