  2nephi,23,11,"And I will punish the world for evil, and the wicked for their iniquity; I will cause the arrogancy of the proud to cease, and will lay down the haughtiness of the terrible.","11:17:Isa. 24:6; Mal. 4:1.|46:52:Ex. 34:7; Prov. 21:12.|107:112:Job 40:11; 2 Ne. 12:12; D&C 64:24."
