  2nephi,23,19,"And Babylon, the glory of kingdoms, the beauty of the Chaldees' excellency, shall be as when God overthrew Sodom and Gomorrah.","4:11:Isa. 14:15 (4–27).|107:112:Gen. 19:24 (24–25); Deut. 29:23; Jer. 49:18; 2 Ne. 13:9."
